# Habit Tracker

## 🧠 Introduction

Habit Tracker is a full-featured web application designed to help users build and maintain positive habits. It allows users to sign up or log in securely, add and manage habits, track streaks, and visualize statistics like completion rate and active streaks. It supports dark mode and real-time updates using Firebase Firestore.

## 🧰 Project Type
**Fullstack**  
- Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript  
- Backend: Firebase Auth & Firestore  
- Database: Firestore NoSQL  

## 🚀 Deployed App
- Frontend: [https://your-deployed-site.web.app](tranquil-custard-666be1.netlify.app)
